attribute.name: name
attribute.value: Example with API, provider and Gogo command Bundle

attribute.name: description
attribute.value: rovides a mapping from Event Admin events to Javascript Server Side Events (SSE). This bundle registers under /sse/1, the remaining path is treated as the topic. It will then send all matching events to the browser through SSE. The type of the event is org.osgi.service.eventadmin;topic=%s, the data payload is a JSON representation of the event properties.
